  m_text: "\nPedro S\xE1nchez V\xE1zquez.\n\nThis game is part of my TFG project
    in Universitat Oberta de Catalunya for my degree on Computer Science and Engineering.
    \n\nDisclaimer: Most art in the game was AI generated using Nano Banana 2.  \n\nI
    respect the work of the wonderful artist out there that create inmersive and
    liveful gaming experiences. However, given my time restrictions and available
    resources as a student and the low expected economical return of the project
    I opted for AI as a source of quick prototype images for the game.\n\nThe original
    game mechanics were taken from Azul boardgame by Kiesling M. \n"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
